Preston was so patient,  answered all our questions and helps us find the right pool for us! The  process was painless and we had everything up and running in 3 weeks! We are super happy with our new pool! We highly recommend them

Pools 123 dfw installed our 35ft pool with spa. Joey our sales and go to guy was very professional and helpful. Aside from a glitch with the handrail and a little communication issue with the scheduler all went well. Pool looks great. Would recommend to anyone looking for a fiberglass pool.
